title: 2020 Maritime Silk Road Culture and Tourism Expo held in E China
content: Representatives from Russia take photos during the 2020 Maritime Silk Road Culture and Tourism Expo (Ningbo China) at Ningbo International Conference and Exhibition Center in Ningbo, east China's Zhejiang Province, Sept. 25, 2020. The expo kicked off here on Sept. 25 and will last till Sept. 27. (Xinhua/Yin Xiaosheng)
